    <h1 class="hero-h">How much does Claude cost <em style="color:#00C853;font-style:italic;">for a business?</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      The short answer: between <strong style="color:#F0FFF0;">$20 and $100 per user per month</strong>, depending on which plan you're on. The longer answer — what you should actually budget when you're seriously deploying Claude across a team — is more useful. Here's the plan-by-plan breakdown plus realistic total-cost-of-adoption numbers.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<section>
  <div class="sec-inner">
    <span class="lbl">The four plans</span>
    <h2 class="h2">Claude pricing tiers, side by side</h2>
    <p class="body">Anthropic offers four plans: Free, Pro, Team, and Enterprise. They differ in usage limits, collaboration features, and admin controls. For most businesses the right starting point is <em>Team</em>.</p>

    <div class="price-grid">

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-tier">Free</div>
        <div class="card-name">Free</div>
        <div class="card-price">$0</div>
        <div class="card-detail">Basic chat, limited daily usage, no Projects, no advanced models. Useful for trying Claude. Not viable for business workflows.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-tier">Individual</div>
        <div class="card-name">Pro</div>
        <div class="card-price">$20<small>/mo</small></div>
        <div class="card-detail">Higher usage limits, all current models including Opus, Claude Projects (the killer feature for business work). $200/yr if billed annually.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card featured">
        <div class="card-tier">Recommended</div>
        <div class="card-name">Team</div>
        <div class="card-price">$30<small>/seat/mo</small></div>
        <div class="card-detail">Pro features plus shared Projects, central billing, admin controls, higher usage caps. Annual billing; 5-seat minimum. $35/seat if billed monthly.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-tier">Enterprise</div>
        <div class="card-name">Enterprise</div>
        <div class="card-price">Custom</div>
        <div class="card-detail">SSO, SCIM, audit logs, extended context windows, dedicated support, custom contracts. Quoted by Anthropic sales; typical floor is $60–$100/seat/mo.</div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="callout">
      <p><strong>Practical guidance:</strong> If you have 1–4 people, Pro is fine. The moment you hit 5 people who all want to share knowledge, jump straight to Team — the shared Projects feature alone justifies the $10/seat premium. Don't reach for Enterprise unless you have compliance or SSO requirements that genuinely block adoption.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
